# weather = pd.read_csv('/content/drive/MyDrive/data/NIW/weather_data_historic.csv')
# weather['Day'] = pd.to_datetime(weather['Day'], dayfirst=True)

# import di data
di = pd.read_csv('/content/drive/MyDrive/data/NIW/di_flow_data.csv')
di['perioddate'] = pd.to_datetime(di['perioddate'], dayfirst=True)

# import leakage data
leak = pd.read_csv('/content/drive/MyDrive/data/NIW/leakage_historic_daily.csv')
leak['N_DATE'] = pd.to_datetime(leak['N_DATE'], dayfirst=True)
# join tables
df = di.copy() #.merge(weather, how='left', left_on='periodDate', right_on='Day')
df = df.merge(leak, how='left', left_on='perioddate', right_on='N_DATE')
df = df.merge(ni_holidays, how='left', left_on='perioddate', right_on='date')
df['holiday'] = df['holiday'].fillna(0)

# drop unnecessary columns/rows and set index
df = df.drop(columns=['N_DATE', 'date', 'Unnamed: 2'])
df = df.dropna()
df = df.set_index('perioddate').asfreq('d')

# rename col and sort out dtypes
df = df.rename(columns={'SUM(CH.DAYLEAK)': 'leak'})

df['leak'] = df['leak'].str.replace(',','')
df['leak'] = df['leak'].astype(float)

# flow data for 06/07/2021 is missing so impute values for that row
for col in df.columns:
  df[col] = df[col].fillna(df[col].mean())

Lag Features¶

In [ ]:
target_map_target = df['di_change'].to_dict()
target_map_leak = df['leak'].to_dict()

def make_lags(df, lags):
  df = df.copy()
  for lag in range(1, lags+1):
    df[f'target_lag_{lag}'] = (df.index - pd.Timedelta(f'{lag} day')).map(target_map_target)
    df[f'leak_lag_{lag}'] = (df.index - pd.Timedelta(f'{lag} day')).map(target_map_leak)
  return df

train_set = make_lags(df, 14)
df.pop('leak')

Date Features¶

In [ ]:
def create_date_features(df):
  df = df.copy()
  df['dayofweek'] = df.index.dayofweek
  df['quarter'] = df.index.quarter
  df['month'] = df.index.month
  df['year'] = df.index.year
  df['dayofyear'] = df.index.dayofyear
  df['dayofmonth'] = df.index.day
  df['weekofyear'] = df.index.week
  return df

Training with Cross Validation¶

In [ ]:
fold = 0
preds = []
actuals = []
scores = []
for train_idx, val_idx in tss.split(train_set):
  train = train_set.iloc[train_idx]
  test = train_set.iloc[val_idx]

  X_train = train.copy()
  y_train = X_train.pop('di_change')

  X_test = test.copy()
  y_test = X_test.pop('di_change')


  reg = xgb(colsample_bytree=1,
                   learning_rate=0.3012688100681574,
                   max_depth=7,
                   n_estimators=5000,
                   reg_alpha=100,
                   reg_lambda=1e-09,
                   subsample=1)

  reg.fit(X_train, y_train,
          eval_set=[(X_train, y_train), (X_test, y_test)],
          verbose=1000)
  
  y_pred = reg.predict(X_test)
  preds.append(y_pred)
  actuals.append(y_test)
  score = np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred))
  scores.append(score)
